title: Infernal
content:
Infernal may refer to:

  • A cape:
    • Infernal cape, a reward from completing the Inferno
    • Infernal max cape, a cosmetic upgrade made by using the infernal cape on a max cape
    • Infernal max hood, a cosmetic upgrade made by using the infernal cape on a max cape
  • Tools created using a smouldering stone:
    • Infernal axe
    • Infernal pickaxe
    • Infernal harpoon
  • Infernal eel
  • Rod Fishing spot (infernal eel)
  • Infernal pyrelord, a superior pyrelord Slayer monster
  • Infernal Mage
  • Infernal chart
  • Infernal Dimensions
 This page is used to distinguish between articles with similar names.
